name: StarTeleTech
overview: At StarTele Tech we specialize in mobile advertising and mobile marketing. We offer a range of products that makes us unique in the digital marketing industry. IP Multimedia Subsystem, IMS, Messaging, Short Messaging System, SMS, SMSC, Text Messaging System, Multimedia Messaging System, MMS, MMSC, Video Services, messaging gateway, fixed-line SMSC, Location, Location Based services, LBS, Fleet management, Friend finder, Buddy Finder, Location based alerts, Mobile Alerts, Push Services, Pull Services, Resource tracking, 3GPP, ETSI, VoIP Product Development. Platforms (SDP) & Next Generation (3G/IMS) Value Added Services (VAS) applications for audio & video ringback tones (RBT), video services, and location-based services (LBS)
